 Though this is obviously a non-functioning unit, it sounds like a great time for anyone with fond memories of rushing home to open up their launch-era Xbox console. It has a removable hard drive, working lights, an interactive interior and a moving disc drive. Mega says there are even more easter eggs for true Xbox die-hards, suggesting that something happens when you insert the fake <em>Halo 3</em> disc into the fake disc drive.</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> The kit includes nearly 1,400 pieces, so the build should take a while, allowing you to revel in the halcyon glow of the mid 2000s. Mega Blok says this set is for ages 18 and up. It releases on October 8 and costs $150, which is half as much as a bare-bones Xbox 360 cost back in 2005. This isn&#39;t the first gaming-themed building set by Mega Blok. In the past, it&#39;s released sets <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2014-02-17-assassins-creed-mega-bloks-will-let-you-build-the-perfect-killi.html">based on Assassin&#39;s Creed</a> and <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2012-10-19-world-of-warcraft-mega-bloks-commercial-airs.html"><em>World of Warcraft,</em></a> among others.</p><p> While it&#39;s debatable if the Xbox 360 was Microsoft&#39;s crowning console achievement, it was certainly the company&#39;s most popular system to-date. The 360 sold 85 million units throughout its run and had a truly impressive games catalog, from the first two Gears of War entries to the Mass Effect trilogy. The console also saw the release of <em>Skyrim, GTA IV, Halo 3</em> and a whole bunch of Call of Duty <em>&nbsp;</em> games. Did we mention <em>Crackdown, Alan Wake</em> and <em>Bioshock?</em> It was a good time to be a gamer. </p><p><core-commerce id="0d28c6fdadee468a910490f82edd6370" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p></p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/this-xbox-360-building-set-is-a-nostalgic-halo-infused-thrill-161350310.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/this-xbox-360-building-set-is-a-nostalgic-halo-infused-thrill-161350310.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> ce5fbcb7-d5da-486c-9966-396f1cbd598e</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 08 Sep 2023 16:13:50 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694191291</ingested><modified> 2023-09-08T16:41:35+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Game Consoles]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="1199" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/08898040-4e60-11ee-bff5-8ad2f01018b8" width="2267"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1199" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/08898040-4e60-11ee-bff5-8ad2f01018b8" width="2267"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Mega Blok]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[An image of the Xbox 360 Mega Blok pack.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Xbox 360 Mega Blok]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Apple event rumor roundup: What to expect at the 'Wonderlust' iPhone 15 keynote]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Apple&#39;s latest <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apples-iphone-15-event-is-set-for-september-12th-161028116.html">fall iPhone event</a> — “Wonderlust” — is nearly here. Four new iPhones and a couple of Apple Watch models are expected to take center stage when the company showcases its latest products. <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-09-29-the-best-usb-c-cables-and-adapters.html">USB-C</a> should be in the spotlight as Apple changes its charging ports in response to <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/iphones-switch-usb-c-comply-eu-charger-law-075020117.html">new EU regulations</a> . Although nothing is set in stone until Tim Cook takes the stage on Tuesday, we&#39;ve gathered the most probable leaks and rumors ahead of Apple&#39;s September 12 event.</p><h2> iPhone 15 and iPhone 15 Pro</h2><p> No matter what else Tim Cook and company reveal, new iPhones are practically guaranteed to dominate the day&#39;s headlines. We can expect a high-end iPhone 15 Pro and iPhone 15 Pro Max, along with a standard iPhone 15 and iPhone 15 Plus. There was an earlier report that Apple may <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/iphone-15-ultra-report-211709352.html">rebrand the Pro Max model as “iPhone 15 Ultra”</a> this year, but it isn&#39;t clear if that&#39;s still on the table. </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="0dadfc0895f24f169e255af8475d6009"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/b8AT6NFhD5s?si=x50xRCIEy183d6OL" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div><p> First, screen sizes will likely stand pat. That means 6.1-inch displays for the iPhone 15 and 15 Pro and 6.7-inch screens for the iPhone 15 Plus and iPhone 15 Pro Max (or “Ultra”). ProMotion, Apple&#39;s branding for <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/iphone-13-pro-and-pro-max-180857712.html">120Hz variable refresh rate displays</a> , will almost certainly remain exclusive to the top-tier models.</p><p> A change many foresee is Lightning cables becoming obsolete. Over a decade has passed since <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2012-09-12-apple-details-new-dock-connector-its-called-lightning.html">switching</a> from 30-pin connectors to Lightning, and European regulations are <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/iphones-switch-usb-c-comply-eu-charger-law-075020117.html">forcing Apple</a> to swap ports again — this time to USB-C. “Obviously, we&#39;ll have to comply” with the EU&#39;s requirements, Apple VP Greg Joswiak <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:8;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/livecoverage/wsj-tech-live-2022/card/apple-says-iphones-will-comply-with-eu-law-requiring-usb-c-charging-ljK6qqmQkOkF2RdnWvrc" data-original-link="https://www.wsj.com/livecoverage/wsj-tech-live-2022/card/apple-says-iphones-will-comply-with-eu-law-requiring-usb-c-charging-ljK6qqmQkOkF2RdnWvrc">confirmed</a> in an interview with the <em>WSJ</em> last year. Although Apple could wait for next year&#39;s iPhone launch to make the EU&#39;s deadline, leaks and well-sourced insiders <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2023-07-30/apple-iphone-15-pro-features-usb-c-port-new-design-thinner-bezels-lkpemg29">indicate</a> almost unanimously that this year&#39;s iPhone 15 will be the one to kick off the USB-C iPhone era. </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/8e4fb8d0-4cf2-11ee-bf67-6db5f94021dc" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/8e4fb8d0-4cf2-11ee-bf67-6db5f94021dc" style="height:1333px;width:2000px;" alt="A hand holding the iPhone 14 Pro smartphone with its Home Screen displayed. A grassy blurred background is behind." data-uuid="efebc606-77a0-3e8f-aa6a-970834c5997f"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Cherlynn Low / Engadget</div></figure><p> However, connected Apple analyst Ming-Chi Kuo <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/mingchikuo/status/1593052344841011201">predicts</a> only the higher-end iPhone models will see faster USB-C data transfer speeds. Kuo believes only the two pro models will support “at least USB 3.2 or Thunderbolt 3” high-speed wired connections, while the two standard models (iPhone 15 / 15 Plus) would use slower USB 2.0 speeds, the same as Lightning. At least some new models could also <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://9to5mac.com/2023/08/17/iphone-15-faster-charging-35w/">support</a> faster (35W) charging speeds, although (predictably, some might say) you could need a proprietary Apple-made adapter to power up at those rates.</p><p> Dynamic Island, the display cutout that Apple launched on the <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-iphone-14-pro-max-review-dynamic-island-useful-always-on-display-battery-life-camera-test-sample-pictures-130020449.html">iPhone 14 Pro / Pro Max</a> , is expected to carry over to all four models in 2023. A replacement for the “notch” on older full-screen iPhones, Dynamic Island is a floating black pill-shaped section just below the top of the screen. It not only masks the phone&#39;s front camera and Face ID sensor, but it can also flash alerts, animations and shortcuts for tasks like driving directions, timers or music. Apple design VP Alan Dye tidily <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.macrumors.com/2022/10/02/iphone-14-pro-dynamic-island-interview/">summarized</a> that Dynamic Island can “display alerts, notifications, and ongoing operations in real-time without seeing the boundary between hardware and software.” </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/6d128c00-4cf3-11ee-adfe-361b7b5c8f63" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/6d128c00-4cf3-11ee-adfe-361b7b5c8f63" style="height:1333px;width:2000px;" alt="Review photography of the iPhone 14 Pro. It's in a person's right hand with the phone's back facing the camera. Western US Greenery blurred in the background behind." data-uuid="63b14323-0e29-3737-8ab9-cfdb49982088"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Cherlynn Low / Engadget</div></figure><p> Stainless steel may go the way of the Lightning port, as the iPhone 15 Pro and Pro Max are rumored to <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/iphone-15-pro-set-to-feature-a-thinner-bezel-titanium-frame-and-usb-c-charging-094118389.html">switch to titanium frames</a> . The material upgrade could make the new pro lineup “stronger, lighter and more premium,” as <em>Bloomberg</em> ’s Mark Gurman <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2023-07-30/apple-iphone-15-pro-features-usb-c-port-new-design-thinner-bezels-lkpemg29">described</a> in July. He said the titanium used in high-end Apple Watch models was “a test for bringing that material to its highest-volume device.” Although the phones are expected to keep the same frosted glass back, their corners could be more rounded than in previous models. In addition, Apple may drop the lineup&#39;s gold hue for a <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://9to5mac.com/2023/08/24/titan-gray-iphone-15-pro/">“titan gray”</a> colorway.</p><p> Thinner bezels are expected to accompany the pro series&#39; titanium frame. Apple is reportedly developing the iPhone 15 Pro / Pro Max displays with a process called low-injection pressure over-molding, or “LIPO.” First used in <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-watch-series-7-review-all-about-the-screen-130036181.html">Apple Watch Series 7</a> manufacturing, Gurman <a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-iphone-15-pro-probably-may-not-feature-solid-state-buttons-as-previously-rumored-174416328.html">reported</a> that the technology could reduce the pro series&#39; bezels to 1.5 mm, down from the 2.2 mm ones found in current models.</p><p> The iPhone 15 Pro series could also have an Action Button like on the <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-watch-ultra-review-battery-life-compass-gps-hike-130055477.html">Apple Watch Ultra</a> . The customizable toggle would replace the mute switch on the upper-left side of the pro-tier iPhones. Possible uses for the Action Button (based on code <a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://www.macrumors.com/2023/07/26/ios-17-beta-action-button-iphone-15-pro/">uncovered</a> in iOS 17) include launching the camera, lighting the phone&#39;s flashlight, activating Focus, opening accessibility features or standing pat with the standard mute function. Sources indicated Apple initially wanted to swap in <a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/iphone-15-solid-state-buttons-ming-chi-kuo-083518207.html">haptic solid-state ones</a> for the iPhone&#39;s physical volume and power buttons, but the company <a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://www.macrumors.com/2023/04/11/kuo-iphone-15-pro-no-solid-state-buttons-after-all/">reportedly</a> canceled the feature after encountering “unresolved technical issues before mass production.” So expect standard volume and power / sleep buttons. </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/2eef1b50-4cf3-11ee-be71-2886bfe4a93b" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/2eef1b50-4cf3-11ee-be71-2886bfe4a93b" style="height:1080px;width:1920px;" alt="Still from the fall 2022 iPhone event. Apple VP Greg Joswiak stands in front of a dark background with purple lettering that reads," data-uuid="86285e4d-e58b-3ba2-9de3-a483e94f3097"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">苹果</div></figure><p>The most likely camera upgrade is a new <a data-i13n="cpos:23;pos:1" href="https://www.macrumors.com/2022/07/14/periscope-lens-iphone-15-pro-max-kuo/">periscope lens</a> exclusive to the iPhone 15 Pro Max (or Ultra). It would use a prism to bend or fold light captured by the sensor, leading to an optical zoom of 5x to 6x without making the phone beefier. The iPhone 14 Pro series supports up to 3x optical zoom.</p><p> One of the surest bets about a new flagship iPhone&#39;s features is a faster, next-generation chip. The iPhone 15 Pro and Pro Max are <a data-i13n="cpos:24;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/iphone-15-pro-set-to-feature-a-thinner-bezel-titanium-frame-and-usb-c-charging-094118389.html">rumored</a> to use a 3nm chip, likely called the A17 Bionic. It would provide performance boosts (and <em>maybe</em> longer battery life). Meanwhile, the iPhone 15 / 15 Plus pair is rumored to repeat what the company did in 2022: recycling last year&#39;s high-end chip. That means the iPhone 15 / 15 Plus would use the A16 Bionic, found in the iPhone 14 Pro.</p><p> If recent years are any indication, the new iPhones would be available for pre-order the Friday after the Apple event, with shipments and general availability kicking off a week later. Although this year&#39;s models may be <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:25;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.macrumors.com/2023/09/04/major-price-hike-rumored-for-iphone-15-pro-models/" data-original-link="https://www.macrumors.com/2023/09/04/major-price-hike-rumored-for-iphone-15-pro-models/">more expensive</a> .</p><h2> Apple Watch Series 9 and <strong>Apple Watch Ultra</strong></h2><p> This could be a minor year for Apple Watch updates. The primary hardware change in the Apple Watch Series 9 is rumored to be an S9 chip, marking the product&#39;s <a data-i13n="cpos:26;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-watch-series-9-may-finally-get-a-new-processor-151516259.html">first real processor upgrade</a> since 2020. Gurman <a data-i13n="cpos:27;pos:1" href="https://discord.com/invite/power-on">reported</a> that the S9 will be based on the A15 chip that debuted in Apple&#39;s iPhone 13 (2021) lineup. The S9&#39;s full details aren&#39;t known, but it&#39;s rumored to move from a 7nm manufacturing process to a denser and more efficient 5nm or 4nm one. Expect performance boosts and (perhaps) longer battery life.</p><p> Reports suggest the new Apple Watch will otherwise be a largely ho-hum update, with Gurman saying this year&#39;s model won&#39;t offer any significant design changes or new features. A pink color option and Bluetooth 5.3 support are possible changes for the new model. Regardless, watchOS 10 — arguably the <a data-i13n="cpos:28;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-apple-watch-embraces-widgets-again-in-watchos-10-180838970.html">biggest software update</a> in the wearable&#39;s history — will likely stand as the biggest advancement for the Apple Watch in 2023. </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/e29e5d10-4cf2-11ee-bbcb-3ded98f0e207" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/e29e5d10-4cf2-11ee-bbcb-3ded98f0e207" style="height:1166px;width:1750px;" alt="Photo of a person wearing the Apple Watch Ultra. Side view taken from the person's right side (they're wearing the watch on their left wrist)." data-uuid="66db99a5-addb-3218-87c3-88a025a9a99d"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Cherlynn Low / Engadget</div></figure><p> As for the Apple Watch Ultra, it&#39;s also expected to receive an incremental 2nd-generation update. In addition to the S9 chip, a new Apple Watch Ultra could add a <a data-i13n="cpos:29;pos:1" href="https://www.macrumors.com/2023/08/01/apple-watch-ultra-2-black-titanium-rumor/">black titanium case</a> . The current model ships in a “natural” color, expected to return alongside the darker option.</p><h2> AirPods </h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/74a118f0-4cf4-11ee-9717-368ef3449654" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/74a118f0-4cf4-11ee-9717-368ef3449654" style="height:1200px;width:2000px;" alt="Photo of a home-engineered USB-C charging case for AirPods." data-uuid="a2105221-1286-380c-aec9-f486c89e6874"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Ken Pillonel</div></figure><p> You probably want to keep your AirPods expectations in check, as the company&#39;s march away from Lightning and towards USB-C will likely be the only headphone upgrades at this year&#39;s Apple event. The company will reportedly launch “new” versions of the current AirPods models, with charging cases that use USB-C instead of Lightning serving as the only difference.</p><p> Rumored changes to the AirPods lineup down the road <a data-i13n="cpos:30;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apples-next-airpods-pro-could-feature-a-built-in-temperature-sensor-162531033.html">include</a> body-temperature sensors, accessibility features for people with hearing disabilities and a potential price drop for the entry-level model. But we won&#39;t likely see any of that on Tuesday.</p><h2>软件</h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/d06d9dc0-4cf4-11ee-9f8d-25fb17d4ec05" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/d06d9dc0-4cf4-11ee-9f8d-25fb17d4ec05" style="height:1125px;width:2000px;" alt="Apple VP Craig Federighi at the WWDC keynote event. He stands inside Apple Park in front of a huge white board that reads" data-uuid="0757d4c2-4e79-336e-828c-11d33814c801"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">苹果</div></figure><p>You can expect the event to bring more details about Apple&#39;s first big software updates of 2023: <a data-i13n="cpos:31;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ios-17-preview-public-beta-facetime-standby-iphone-120025938.html">iOS 17</a> , <a data-i13n="cpos:32;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-apple-watch-embraces-widgets-again-in-watchos-10-180838970.html">watchOS 10</a> and (possibly) <a data-i13n="cpos:33;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ipados-17-preview-a-smoother-multitasking-experience-for-those-who-really-need-it-173022677.html">iPadOS 17</a> . Apple announced the operating systems at <a data-i13n="cpos:34;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/heres-everything-apple-announced-at-wwdc-2023-223303827.html">WWDC 2023</a> , and their final versions should become available to the public sometime between the event and the iPhone 15 launch. Following recent years&#39; patterns, <a data-i13n="cpos:35;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/macos-sonoma-preview-widgets-screen-savers-210036486.html">macOS Sonoma</a> will likely launch in October — with iPadOS 17 joining if it isn&#39;t included alongside iOS 17. A potential October Apple event could <a data-i13n="cpos:36;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-is-reportedly-testing-m3-chips-for-new-macs-arriving-this-fall-173457588.html">consist of</a> new iMac, MacBook Air and 13-inch MacBook Pro models running the M3 chip.</p><p> iOS 17 includes a new StandBy mode, voicemail transcriptions, FaceTime video voicemails, contact posters, NameDrop and new in-line predictive text suggestions (among <a data-i13n="cpos:37;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apples-ios-17-revamps-core-apps-172548767.html">other additions</a> ). Meanwhile, watchOS 10 is arguably the platform&#39;s most significant update since the wearable&#39;s 2015 launch. The new software changes the Apple Watch&#39;s fundamental control scheme: The side button now activates Control Center (instead of recent apps or the dock), and twisting the watch&#39;s Digital Crown from the watch face scrolls through a customizable stack of glanceable widgets.</p><p> You can read more about the upcoming software in Engadget&#39;s previews of <a data-i13n="cpos:38;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ios-17-preview-public-beta-facetime-standby-iphone-120025938.html">iOS 17</a> , <a data-i13n="cpos:39;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ipados-17-preview-a-smoother-multitasking-experience-for-those-who-really-need-it-173022677.html">iPadOS 17</a> and <a data-i13n="cpos:40;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-apple-watch-embraces-widgets-again-in-watchos-10-180838970.html">watchOS 10</a> coverage.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/what-to-expect-at-apples-wonderlust-iphone-15-event-181545715.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/what-to-expect-at-apples-wonderlust-iphone-15-event-181545715.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 07ae7b84-d201-4dbc-8d1f-24d469d82984</guid><dc:creator> Will Shanklin</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 08 Sep 2023 16:00:40 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694188859</ingested><modified> 2023-09-08T16:01:06+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/bcbf7f80-4cf1-11ee-afd8-ca93262b7fa7" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/bcbf7f80-4cf1-11ee-afd8-ca93262b7fa7" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Apple]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Screenshot of Tim Cook presenting at Apple's September 2022 iPhone launch event. He stands outdoors at Apple Park, on green grass in front of the "spaceship" building, holding two hands in front of him to emphasize a point.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Tim Cook]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Apple's Monarch: Legacy of Monsters trailer pits Kurt Russell against Godzilla]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/apple/">苹果</a>公司涉足许多领域，现在它正通过即将推出的电视节目进军怪兽业务。该公司发布了<em>《君主：怪物的遗产》</em>的第一部预告片，虽然标题可能不太清楚， <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/godzilla-is-headed-to-apple-tv-in-the-monster-verses-first-live-action-series-181010114.html">但这在很大程度上是一部哥斯拉系列</a>。</p><p>该剧改编自<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2015-10-14-godzilla-and-king-kong-will-share-one-cinematic-universe.html">传奇影业的怪兽宇宙</a>，并与该工作室最近的<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/godzilla/">哥斯拉</a>电影联系在一起。故事的部分背景是哥斯拉与泰坦之间的一场战斗，这场战斗摧毁了旧金山的大部分地区，但它发生在三代人的时间里。现实生活中的父子库尔特·拉塞尔和怀亚特·拉塞尔在不同的时代扮演同一角色，陆军军官李·肖。肖遇到了一对兄弟姐妹，他们正在探索他们的家族与追踪哥斯拉、金刚和其他巨型野兽的神秘组织君主的联系。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>预告片并没有透露太多关于这部剧的信息，只是展示了标志性怪物（包括一个让人想起<em>《侏罗纪公园》</em>中第一次遭遇霸王龙的镜头）、一些演员的动作和被毁坏的旧金山。但<em>《君主：怪物的遗产》</em>似乎确实会包含影迷们在电影中所欣赏的大部分奇观。您可以在 11 月 17 日观看该季共 10 集的前两集，并且在 1 月 12 日之前每周都会在<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/apple-tv-plus/">Apple TV+</a>上推出新的一集。 </p><div id="3cf82c810a4546bcacc5fe2bbcb77fda"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ec27RCzb6qI?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/apples-monarch-legacy-of-monsters-trailer-pits-kurt-russell-against-godzilla-154145455.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apples-monarch-legacy-of-monsters-trailer-pits-kurt-russell-against-godzilla-154145455.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 223c0901-c953-4fc7-8894-6c3a7d7ea03c</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 08 Sep 2023 15:41:45 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694188536</ingested><modified> 2023-09-08T15:55:44+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Celebrities]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="2160" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/0e5f2f10-4e60-11ee-b5fd-ba15a574fafc" width="3840"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2160" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/0e5f2f10-4e60-11ee-b5fd-ba15a574fafc" width="3840"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Apple TV+]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Godzilla roars at a person standing next to a school bus in Apple TV+ series Monarch: Legacy of Monsters.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Monarch: Legacy of Monsters]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best audio interfaces in 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>无论您制作音乐、播客、流媒体还是只是喜欢听这些内容，良好的音频接口都会让一切变得不同。 Mac 或 PC 的内置声音足以满足大多数日常任务的需要，但对于创作者来说，它可能无法满足您录音所需的声音。</p><p>好消息是，有大量针对各种特定需求和用例量身定制的选项。不太好的消息是，尝试决定哪一个最适合您可能会有点不知所措。这就是我们编写本指南的原因，其中我们强调了最佳选择，无论您只是想录制吉他，还是想向数千名观众现场直播（或者至少在您处理该数字时听起来不错）。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>不用担心被术语淹没，我们将专注于正在处理的任务而不是 kHz 和分贝，以便您知道哪一个最适合您想要的结果，而不会让您感觉像是刚从数学课上出来。</p><h2>最适合预算有限的人</h2><p>音频接口不仅仅适合创作者。也许您在家工作并希望能够使用高品质 XLR 麦克风进行工作通话。或者您可能更喜欢对耳机和麦克风进行物理控制？或者，您可能只是欣赏专用设备比 PC 附带的设备所提供的卓越音频质量。如果是这样，您可能不需要花太多钱 - 这里有三个不会让您倾家荡产的选择。</p><h3> M-Audio M-Track 独奏</h3><p><core-commerce id="42e15f34b92c43d3bd53bcb3b44c4aab" data-type="product-list"></p><p>它当然不是这个列表中最漂亮的设备，但<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVVdrwbc7Ex7wOgGhwNnAm89tVEd3bP9IViJvMFmh_ta&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FM-Audio-M-Track-Solo-Interface-Podcasting%2Fdp%2FB08Q1NJSBQ%3F">M-Track Solo</a> （49 美元）在美观方面的不足，它的功能性足以弥补价格的不足。如果您只是在寻找可以插入麦克风或吉他（或同时插入两者）的东西，那么 M-Track Solo 是无可比拟的。</p><p>对于初学者或想要成为播客的人来说，还有<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9NLUF1ZGlvLU0tVHJhY2stRHVvLUludGVyZmFjZS1Qb2RjYXN0aW5nL2RwL0IwOFExVjc3TlI_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tdzgtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjRmYzRjNTUxLTE2ZWMtNGJlMi1hNGY5LWFiNzBmMTQzNTZmZCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAARt2DPICSc8L0WKcfNIA7plLHJWIgHQ1TUlQ0COZbCgk&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FM-Audio-M-Track-Duo-Interface-Podcasting%2Fdp%2FB08Q1V77NR">M-Track Duo</a> （70 美元），它增加了第二个 XLR 麦克风连接，这样您就可以邀请客人过来并将其录制到他们自己的频道上，从而使编辑变得更加容易 - 而且您不需要当您共用麦克风时与他们变得亲密。这里没有太多的装饰，比如 MIDI 或效果器，但就价格而言，它是一个不错的选择。</p><h3> Presonos AudioBox iOne</h3><p><core-commerce id="5c3dfa4075d040f5a74871ac7a200224" data-type="product-list"></p><p>与显卡等其他 PC 组件不同，数字声音具有天然的局限性，这意味着旧设备在今天仍然适用，而且价格往往更优惠。 <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAS893qjVKDOT-3v7vRRmGcCAQdcVe0cF7eCb7Udc6ceR&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPreSonus-AudioBox-iOne-Audio-Interface%2Fdp%2FB00KBMAJU8%3Fth%3D1">Presonos 的 AudioBox iOne</a> （70 美元）就是这样的一个例子。它主要面向使用音乐软件的创作者，但它是一款出色的全能音频接口，具有所有必要的连接功能，而且价格现已降低。</p><p>作为奖励，AudioBox iOne 也可以与 iPad 很好地配合 - 在这个价位上不能保证。尽管有些人可能会发现耳机放大效果偏低，但如果这对您来说很重要的话。</p><h3> Focusrite 斯嘉丽 独奏</h3><p><core-commerce id="99ce79c958fc458caccd715e83dad22b" data-type="product-list"></p><p>Focusrite 的 Scarlett 系列接口出现在如此多的推荐列表中是有原因的 - 其中有两个位置：它们在性能、可靠性和价格之间实现了良好的平衡。 <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9Gb2N1c3JpdGUtU2NhcmxldHQtQXVkaW8tSW50ZXJmYWNlLVRvb2xzL2RwL0IwN1FSNloxSkI_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tdzgtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjRmYzRjNTUxLTE2ZWMtNGJlMi1hNGY5LWFiNzBmMTQzNTZmZCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAATwL6gxLlFBmKAdaOPsQrUvQ03Tr_aPcd97uhSeST1HD&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFocusrite-Scarlett-Audio-Interface-Tools%2Fdp%2FB07QR6Z1JB">Solo</a>的价格约为 130 美元，并不是你能找到的最便宜的，但它可以让你开始流媒体、播客等。事实上，如果您只是想要<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/advanced-podcast-buyers-guide-part-1-143053492.html">一个 XLR 麦克风</a>端口、改进的耳机放大功能以及轻松连接扬声器，那么 Solo 可能是您唯一需要的接口，它不会让您感觉功能不足，甚至随着您的需求的变化也不会感到动力不足。</p><h2>最适合主播</h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/bc128150-e9c2-11ed-bb8f-9e0d10d1f919" style="height:1333px;" alt="四个用于流媒体的音频接口彼此相邻。" data-uuid="ab96c5f0-1e44-321f-84de-e18777f69459"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">詹姆斯·特鲁 / Engadget 摄</div></figure><p>也许并不奇怪，就音频接口而言，流媒体类别是最繁忙的类别之一。部分原因是大多数 Twitchers 和 YouTube 用户需要同时管理多个不同的音频源。因此，此类产品附带一个软件组件，可让您将麦克风、群聊和游戏音频传输到不同的地方。值得庆幸的是，这并不像听起来那么令人困惑——至少对于以下设备之一来说是这样。</p><h3>罗兰·布里奇演员表</h3><p><core-commerce id="1a27fb5eceb943df83d3ee9dc3670e0c" data-type="product-list"></p><p>Roland 可能以其音乐设备而闻名，但该公司还涉足流媒体设备， <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Sweetwater Sound;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=e54dc56f-69db-417f-9610-572a1a179058&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Sweetwater+Sound&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVQ0ee97fDRMl47lh2vCQ0y1niOW1CwS-6wuKgYbzvOk&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sweetwater.com%2Fstore%2Fdetail%2FBridgeCast--roland-bridge-cast-dual-bus-gaming-audio-mixer">Bridge Cast</a> （299 美元）是该类别中最强的设备之一。有四个硬件音量旋钮，因此您可以实时调整麦克风、聊天和游戏等的混音，您甚至可以为您和您的观众实时控制单独的“子混音”。</p><p>在混音控件之上，还有一些语音效果、麦克风均衡器和专用静音按钮 - 这些也可用于触发样本。通过选择通过辅助端口输入电话音频，Roland 为<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/roland-bridge-cast-audio-streaming-interface-220058414.html">Bridge Cast</a>作为流媒体的首选接口提供了有力的支持。</p><h3> TC Helicon GoXLR 迷你</h3><p><core-commerce id="6ce394eb13dc46c48b69f64e2f9944eb" data-type="product-list"></p><p>最初的 GoXLR 是最早真正关注流媒体需求的音频接口之一。 <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAR8LEfFHnntDgcD_8FKowtLop_UUn09F6_OKn1lslCgn&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FHelicon-Online-Broadcast-Interface-Preamp%2Fdp%2FB07XH41DLN">Mini</a>于一年后发布，本身就很受欢迎，并且在首次发布很久之后至今仍然很受欢迎。物理推子可让您对流的每个部分进行触觉控制，连接性包括耳机端口旁边的 3.5 毫米麦克风端口 - 非常适合使用分离器的游戏耳机。</p><p>其他功能包括 !@#$?* 按钮，当您的语言变得有点刺激时，可以让您的观众免受伤害；还有光纤端口，让您的游戏机音频听起来原始。当然，推子上有 RGB 灯光，这几乎与连接性一样重要，对吧？</p><h3>埃尔加托 Wave XLR</h3><p><core-commerce id="8c85ff36c15b4a79a937ac671bc515c8" data-type="product-list"></p><p>如果您没有预算，或者，让我们面对现实，没有足够的桌面空间来放置全尺寸调音台来控制您的流媒体， <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZmxGUR8zfqZe1xpP2u7L03WA5GQVOMzwFDEsnDPHcKJ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FElgato-Wave-Tap-Mute-Mac%2Fdp%2FB09738CKKX">Elgato 的 Wave XLR</a>是极简主义者的选择。它不仅谨慎，而且仅通过一个可点击的旋钮和一个电容式静音按钮就可以实现许多功能。</p><p>尽管简单，Wave XLR 仍然可以提供清脆、清晰的音频。不过，它真正发挥作用的地方在于它与其他 Elgato 产品的模块化集成。例如，当与<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9FbGdhdG8tU3RyZWFtLURlY2stTUstMi1Db250cm9sbGVyL2RwL0IwOTczOENWMkc_cmVmXz1hc3Rfc3RvX2RwJnRhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLXc4LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI0ZmM0YzU1MS0xNmVjLTRiZTItYTRmOS1hYjcwZjE0MzU2ZmQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAW8jyrcVnWAh0DyGkUKghFlSW6oDqbHH2G8NMxYWwAqe&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FElgato-Stream-Deck-MK-2-Controller%2Fdp%2FB09738CV2G%3Fref_%3Dast_sto_dp">Stream Deck</a>和 Wave Link 应用程序配合使用时，体验将开放，包括运行音频插件和创建自定义快捷方式来控制流上的音频的能力。</p><h3> Beacn 混合创建</h3><p><core-commerce id="c422ef7d640f41d099c2225912ea66b2" data-type="product-list"></p><p>如果您已经拥有一个令您满意的音频接口，但又希望为您的流媒体提供方便的混音器，那么 Beacn 的<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAa_jzFEfUIi3qoiX9rNHIYE4q9-DN878yxfon6I1dfBs&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBEACN-submixes-Creators-Streaming-Podcasting%2Fdp%2FB09DJL6CBV">Mix Create</a>正是您所需要的。这款轻量级 USB 混音器配有屏幕，但操作的大脑是为麦克风、游戏、浏览器等创建单独的音频源的软件。</p><p>对于主播来说，这意味着手动控制和子混音的灵活性（即您听到的混音和这里的混音听众可以不同）。对于那些已经拥有硬件接口的人来说，这不仅是一个优雅的解决方案，而且意味着当您不进行直播时，您可以享受 YouTube 和 Spotify 等专用音量控制。</p><h2>最适合音乐家</h2><p>无论您是拨弦还是放 DJ 炸弹，您都需要专业工具为您提供所有正确的端口，同时为您的家庭工作室提供丰富、完美的声音。与希望能够使用来自各种<em>数字</em>源的音频的流媒体不同，音乐家和词曲作者也希望实时录制（和聆听）物理乐器 - 因此我们所有的选择都注重干净的音质良好的连接性。</p><h3> Focusrite 斯嘉丽 2i2</h3><p><core-commerce id="85dc32be596640b78fc240a860c25174" data-type="product-list"></p><p> Focusrite 在这个列表中的第二个展示是一个红色的小盒子，一旦你意识到它，你就会开始看到从直播到 YouTube 吉他教程的任何地方。 <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9Gb2N1c3JpdGUtU2NhcmxldHQtQXVkaW8tSW50ZXJmYWNlLVRvb2xzL2RwL0IwN1FSNzNUNjY_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tdzgtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjRmYzRjNTUxLTE2ZWMtNGJlMi1hNGY5LWFiNzBmMTQzNTZmZCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAX3RLAtzBaDd6pQHzrsmWQDIXXzqOzKIUhG-jaspxACj&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFocusrite-Scarlett-Audio-Interface-Tools%2Fdp%2FB07QR73T66">Scarlett 音频接口</a>的流行不仅仅在于其亮丽的红色外观。前置放大器——将你的声音或乐器变成可用声音的部分——被广泛认为是这个价格范围内音乐制作中最干净的部分。</p><p>具有两个组合端口（此处没有 MIDI），连接性相当标准，但吉他手、歌手和配音演员尤其会